<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ١ ... سُورَةُ الفَاتِحَةِ ... آياتها ٧ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>* ... <span class="c3">{أَعُوذُ}</span> ... أَلْتَجِئُ وَأَعْتَصِمُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* ... <span class="c3">{الرَّجِيمِ}</span> ... الْمَرْجُومِ، المُبْعَدِ مِنْ رَحْمَةِ اللهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِسْمِ اللهِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> أَبْتَدِئُ قِرَاءَتِي مُسْتَعِينًا بِاسْمِ اللهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الرَّحْمنِ}</span> ... الَّذِي وَسِعَتْ رَحْمَتُهُ جَمِيعَ الْخَلْقِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الرَّحِيمِ}</span> ... الَّذِي يَرْحَمُ المُؤمِنِينَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَبِّ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> الرَّبُّ:</span> المُرَبِّي لِخَلْقِهِ بِنِعَمِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْعَالَمِينَ}</span> ... كُلِّ مَنْ سِوَى اللهِ تَعَالَى.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَوْمِ الدِّينِ}</span> ... يَوْمِ الجَزَاءِ وَالحِسَابِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِيَّاكَ نَعْبُدُ}</span> ... لَا نَعْبُدُ إِلَّا أَنْتَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وإِيَّاكَ نَسْتَعِينُ}</span> ... لَا نَسْتَعِينُ فِي قَضَاءِ حَوَائِجِنَا إِلَّا بِكَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الصِّرَاطَ المُستَقِيمَ}</span> ... الطَّرِيقَ الَّذِي لَا عِوَجَ فِيهِ؛ وَهُوَ الإِسْلَامُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَيرِ المَغضُوبِ عَلَيهِمْ}</span> ... الْيَهُودِ، وَمَنْ شَابَهَهُمْ فِي تَرْكِ الْعَمَلِ بِالْعِلْمِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الضَّالِّينَ}</span> ... النَّصَارَى، وَمَنْ شَابَهَهُمْ فِي الْعَمَلِ بِغَيْرِ عِلْمٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>